HEADWORD: Macropod
<hw>Mac"ro*pod</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Macro-</ets>
+ <ets>-pod</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>Any one of a group of
